<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="64">Nesting.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="11" pageNumber="64">Nesting in large aggregations of up to 1,000 or more nests in level friable soil, nest multicellular, sloping burrow in friable soil, the main shaft terminating in a spur, provisioning progressive. Notable for exhibiting nest sharing.</paragraph>
